+5s say speaker="Gino Canessa" text="All right, next I have a batch of five editorial items that I'd like to handle together if there are no objections. These are: FHIR-30670 — remove outdated text from subscription introduction. FHIR-30893 — fix the of-type modifier typo in a search example. FHIR-34735 — fix URL pattern examples. FHIR-27897 — fix Quick Start heading inconsistencies. And FHIR-30515 — add dependsOn field documentation for $translate when used with subscription parameters."
+3s say speaker="Gino Canessa" text="All five are editorial, non-substantive changes. Proposed disposition for all: persuasive, applied. I've already made the changes in the build and they're in the CI preview."
+2s say speaker="Lloyd McKenzie" text="Any objections to handling these as a block?"
